OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,FJersey has become the first non-member
OL,7,Fof the United Nations (UN) to host
OL,8,Finternational talks, addressing
OL,9,Fhumanitarian aid for those in crisis.
OL,11,FThe island was selected to co-chair
OL,12,Fthe UN Office for the Coordination of
OL,13,FHumanitarian Affairs (OCHA) Pooled
OL,14,FFund Working Group (PFWG) to discuss
OL,15,Fhow smaller donors can reach the most
OL,16,Fseverely affected countries through a
OL,17,Fcoordinated approach.
