OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,FOfficials from across the globe have
OL,7,Fjoined discussions which include key
OL,8,Fdecisions on how taxpayers' money in
OL,9,FJersey can provide life-saving support.
OL,11,FEdward Lewis, Executive Director of
OL,12,FJersey Overseas Aid, explains: "Jersey
OL,13,Fis seen in the international sector;
OL,14,Fthey wouldn't come here if they didn't
OL,15,Fthink we had something to say and
OL,16,Fsomething to contribute.
