OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,F"The whole idea is widening the donor
OL,7,Fbase and getting a broader
OL,8,Fconstituency, which is really
OL,9,Fimportant in terms of having an
OL,10,Feffective response.
OL,12,F"And for the next couple of days at
OL,13,Fleast, Jersey is going to play a
OL,14,Fleading role."
OL,16,FCurrently, the island allocates
OL,17,Fapproximately 0.3% of its budget to
OL,18,Foverseas aid - more than #17 million.
