OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,FJersey Overseas Aid has also sent more
OL,7,Fthan #7 million of aid to countries
OL,8,Fincluding Sudan, Syria, and Ukraine
OL,9,Fsince 2016.
OL,11,FDavid Throp, Chief of the UN Office
OL,12,Ffor the Coordination of Humanitarian
OL,13,FAffairs (OCHA), says: "The system as a
OL,14,Fwhole has been going through financial
OL,15,Fdifficulties.
OL,17,F"We have seen cuts from big players,
OL,18,Fsuch as the Americans and other big
OL,19,FEuropean countries; every pound helps
OL,20,Fus save another life.
