OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,F"By putting the money together, we can
OL,7,Fdo something bigger, better, more
OL,8,Fthought-out, and more influential on
OL,9,Fthe beneficiaries and populations
OL,10,Fwe're trying to assist.
OL,12,F"Jersey has been very good at bringing
OL,13,Fleadership to the discussions. The
OL,14,Fisland has been punching above its
OL,15,Fweight in guiding us."
OL,17,FAlice Armanni-Sequi, one of the senior
OL,18,FUN officials, says she's enjoyed the
OL,19,Ftalks in Jersey so far, adding that
OL,20,Fgetting the pooled funds right is
OL,21,Fvital for those in need.
