OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,FShe explains: "We cover a range from
OL,7,Ffood, shelter, health services, water,
OL,8,Fwhich is so critical and nutrition.
OL,10,F"The list goes on, but the formula
OL,11,Fwill depend on the location, so the
OL,12,Fgreat thing about the pooled funds is
OL,13,Fthat we can really come up with the
OL,14,Fright recipe at the local level that
OL,15,Freally represents what people need."
OL,17,FDavid adds: "Most of the funds, in
OL,18,Fparticular the larger funds, are
OL,19,Flocated in some of the more protracted
OL,20,Femergencies.
