OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,F"We do have countries like the
OL,7,Fdemocratic Republic of Congo, Sudan,
OL,8,FSouth Sudan, Afghanistan, the occupied
OL,9,FPalestinian territories, where it is
OL,10,Fnot a sudden onset and a quick finish
OL,11,F- a more fundamental structural
OL,12,Fproblem in the society.
OL,14,F"The good thing about the model is
OL,15,Fthat we can put these funds in place
OL,16,Fand phase them out as and when needed,
OL,17,Fdepending on the changes in the
OL,18,Fsituation."
