OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,FMazen Fadhl Maddi represents the Field
OL,7,FMedical Foundation (FMF) Yemen, and
OL,8,Fknows first hand how overseas aid is a
OL,9,Flifeline for those who need it.
OL,11,FHe explains: "It saves lives. I have
OL,12,Fseen it personally - I have gone to
OL,13,Fthe camps.
OL,15,F"We are also giving communities
OL,16,Fresilience. The money translates into
OL,17,Fa lot of sectors, a lot of assistance,
OL,18,Fsuch as food assistance and nutrition.
OL,19,FWe have huge numbers of acute
OL,20,Fmalnutrition in Yemen."
