OL,3,CJersey hosts UN officials in first of
OL,4,Cits kind meeting on humanitarian aid
OL,6,FChair of Jersey Overseas Aid
OL,7,FCommission, Carolyn Labey, says that
OL,8,Fwhile Jersey's contribution increases
OL,9,Fin line with the island's GDP,
OL,10,Fcontributions can go further.
OL,12,FShe says: "We have connected our
OL,13,Fbudget to GDP, so when the economy
OL,14,Fgrows, our budget grows.
OL,16,F"Our budget is currently fixed at 0.3%
OL,17,Fof GDP, and that isn't quite the OECD
OL,18,Faverage, which is 0.36%.
OL,20,F"The overall aim is to reach 0.7%, but
OL,21,Fthere is a way to go there."
